videos.description: North Carolina opens the scoring against archrival Duke when Mitch Trubisky finds Thomas Jackson open in the corner of the end zone for a 16-yard strike to give the Tar Heels a 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: UNC strikes first with 16-yard TD to Jackson

videos.description: Mitch Trubisky throws his second touchdown pass of the first quarter, this one to Bug Howard, to double North Carolina's lead to 14-0 over Duke.
videos.headline: UNC strikes again as Trubisky hits Howard for the TD

videos.description: After spotting North Carolina a 14-point lead, Duke gets on the board when Daniel Jones fights his way into the end zone from eight yards out.
videos.headline: Jones' keeper gets Duke in the end zone

videos.description: After giving up the first 14 points to North Carolina, Duke answers with back-to-back touchdowns, the latest from Shaun Wilson to level the game at 14-14.
videos.headline: Duke back in the game with Wilson's TD plunge

videos.description: Daniel Jones scores his second rushing touchdown of the game, this time from one-yard out, to bring Duke back level with North Carolina again at 21-21.
videos.headline: Duke completely buys the fake, UNC scores 54-yard TD

videos.description: Daniel Jones scores his second rushing touchdown of the game, this time from one-yard out, to bring Duke back level with North Carolina again at 21-21.
videos.headline: Duke caps off 10-play drive with second Jones TD

videos.description: Tar Heel head coach Larry Fedora discusses the change of playing a factor in the game
videos.headline: Tar Heel head coach Larry Fedora discusses the change of playing a factor in the game

videos.description: Mitch Trubisky pass intercepted Deondre Singleton return for no gain to the Duke 20
videos.headline: Deondre Singleton intercepts Mitch Trubisky to give Duke the ball back

videos.description: Already with two rushing touchdowns, Daniel Jones fakes the run at the goal line and throws instead to Davis Koppenhaver for the score giving Duke the lead at 28-24.
videos.headline: Jump pass to Koppenhaver puts Duke in front

videos.description: Will Kline kickoff for 65 yds , T.J. Logan return for 75 yds to the Duke 25
videos.headline: T.J Logan gives the Heels a spark with this 75-yard kickoff return

videos.description: Mitch Trubisky pass intercepted Alonzo Saxton II return for no gain to the NCaro 44
videos.headline: Mitch Trubisky throws a critical interception that could cost the Heels the Victory Bell

videos.description: Duke Head Coach breaks down what went right in Duke's 28-27 upset win over UNC
videos.headline: Duke Head Coach breaks down what went right in Duke's 28-27 upset win over UNC

videos.description: Breaking down Duke's 28-27 upset win over UNC
videos.headline: Breaking down Duke's 28-27 upset win over UNC

videos.description: Check out Duke's dramatic one-point upset over North Carolina during Thursday night's game at Wallace Wade Stadium.
videos.headline: Blue Devils upset Tar Heels by 1
